snippet.title: Shadow of the Tomb Raider - The Path Home
snippet.description:
The Path Home follows the end of Shadow of the Tomb Raider. With the battle over but allies gone missing, Lara must search for them while uncovering an ancient hidden mystery. Learn more at: https://TombRaider.Games/4112

Subscribe to our channel to keep up-to-date with all things Tomb Raider and Lara Croft: https://www.youtube.com/user/tombraider?sub_confirmation=1
